  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e87f6da9-503a-46c9-b99a-0275e7f806ea\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-62df65b2-6fc5-4cc1-9324-2adea97babdd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-d7954146-6089-4761-9cfd-c876086f5747\">안녕하세요! </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-26acd795-086f-46d4-b947-4217df16eea1\"><b>남성역에 위치한 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5ac5f629-21ae-45c9-9168-a19117237346\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8e8d90ba-bd3a-4fdd-b248-b4271ccd24d2\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-78046e1d-a3d6-4697-8620-fb3bd147dac2\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-2282605a-aa8a-4c03-a113-528f134d8f16\">입니다!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-e87f6da9-503a-46c9-b99a-0275e7f806ea\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d30376cc-fff4-4c62-a556-dd4c04c71d5c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"8\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_8.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7138233e-279f-45a5-859a-a41a8cd89bea\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-370ca0ce-09b7-40f1-a5a4-41584e9cced4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-82768074-4ee9-4853-b9df-3fbbf0676014\">한의학에서는 사람의 건강을 단편적으로 보지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-368807d1-a798-4364-9637-fe348442fba1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1c493540-3664-4718-a87a-e3b43383c44d\">하나의 증상이라 해도 그 원인은 전신의 불균형에서 찾습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c1b57316-d320-452b-abb6-cf67eaf49976\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-77eda556-b2db-462d-9927-861efdbac066\">입 안의 잇몸이 약해지거나 입 속이 자주 헐고, 피가 나는 것 역시 단순한 국소 문제로만 보지 않습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-defb528f-83dd-4b3d-9fec-dbbf2c81216b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f26f75ff-b865-4d13-9908-3b05bf2b598c\">이는 신체 깊은 곳에서 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4c447d6a-c0c6-40f8-9843-0e5ec9d0253c\"><b>노화가 진행 중이라는 신호</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3a31a1c9-a8bc-4da9-aff7-358aec70e176\">일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7138233e-279f-45a5-859a-a41a8cd89bea\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-15d2d002-a596-45cc-88b5-01e50c4708e1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0743c95b-74c9-4c04-86c5-9bc2e43f7832\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0743c95b-74c9-4c04-86c5-9bc2e43f7832\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c7c8e0d8cecbb3d8.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c7c8e0d8cecbb3d8.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c7c8e0d8cecbb3d8.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-0743c95b-74c9-4c04-86c5-9bc2e43f7832\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a34c3357-e6ff-40a8-bc80-f4b489a0b6b9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d4c23f9e-aedf-4197-99d8-0674a05b7abd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c5d22cf6-bdbb-4056-bf69-53a5679e0bae\"><b>고치법이란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a47772de-5201-4fa4-b15c-260856f38327\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf19af22-01d1-4bcf-b4ee-19574a444db4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0bae15e7-1dc3-4a0e-b2be-c8dba322ae9c\">고치법은 전통 한의학에서 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-10ae2b02-93cf-4427-bd51-2ba70ad80132\"><b>몸속 에너지의 근원인 ‘신장(腎)’을 보강하고, 전신의 기혈 흐름을 바로잡는 치료 방법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1d0578a3-7341-4f6a-81a1-199138ff7b93\">입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d8d01f59-f8fb-49b1-852a-302ce061b937\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-068fd560-bcfe-4f62-911d-5c7990f3941e\">신장은 한의학에서 생명력과 관련된 장기로, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-af966e34-7012-44ef-895b-60842725f674\"><b>노화의 속도, 뼈·뇌·호르몬 기능까지도 좌우</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9f943f31-837b-4036-a6b9-7a8fe326feba\">한다고 여겨집니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-55079ce3-3648-49b3-8dec-b6b37f96b6df\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4f76934c-d5ad-4afc-8482-6037da170bfa\">고치법은 주로 다음과 같은 상황에 쓰입니다:</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e14c6eb1-c4e4-470c-bcef-07e1aa400755\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b2cacbb7-2e55-45e6-ad09-6831a52328cc\">나이 들며 입안이 건조하고 시림이 잦을 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a950630-2ead-431e-a1c9-e90b6df7e8fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5ed8bf2a-ba3b-4f4f-b881-2c046aa3a4f1\">피곤하면 얼굴이 잘 붓고 턱 주변이 뻐근할 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94edc9f7-7e0c-4e4f-a046-4d4d75660820\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dc3d8896-2beb-4966-a51c-a05c40e86579\">잇몸에서 자주 열감이 올라오거나 구취가 심할 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bd9db738-c86c-4fad-abfe-4b7221e0cbf2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f77ebb56-94bd-40d5-ad24-24c77c6cc647\">음식을 씹거나 삼킬 때 기력이 빠지는 느낌이 들 때</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-086d38e9-55d4-4ba1-a8fc-ad4a54b2b599\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-67bb1333-3379-4ce3-bad7-ae0b18dd7613\">이 모든 증상은 겉보기엔 작아 보여도, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-463c8204-5b2f-4bb0-9aae-68475e72d0bd\"><b>몸 전체의 기능 저하와 노화</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4741b24d-d4af-4368-b18d-a993078cd9ed\">와 연결돼 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e98620d3-614b-42cc-b737-9b7b659bd3c8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-551f6aa6-aa0e-41d7-ae0b-9918a62b2fcd\">고치법은 이처럼 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6c714479-36e2-4d5e-b9b3-9bff018234fd\"><b>작은 증상을 통해 전신의 에너지를 회복시키는 치료의 시작점</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7aa75141-5165-4283-8270-d6798089c370\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a47772de-5201-4fa4-b15c-260856f38327\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-bd8ddb97-c75d-460d-b55c-d9b22061f4a3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dbf7ea72-ffbb-449e-83e8-a2922d5d7ff7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-426aedcd-2938-4248-b89a-8489ef72a7f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-863f485d-c585-4c27-92c8-9409b6c6b34e\"><b>💡 고치법의 실제 구성</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fd9f146b-b3d0-4731-a7c3-7a00c8f56d5f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9fbd25ff-37bc-401a-a8a7-ca04b03179e3\">고치법은 크게 **보신(補腎)**과 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ff34afcb-dec9-43e6-8e6a-f7f45617983c\"><b>청열해독(淸熱解毒)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-750b405b-7812-435a-ae59-b417f6139761\">, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7a34f11a-ddac-4dee-9c99-041ae46f14f9\"><b>기혈순환 조절</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-71cbc423-7d39-4e55-a5a6-213ab268cf31\">의 세 축으로 이뤄집니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-631661b8-46a7-4a73-832f-03948a389fa3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8d701180-0a87-43a2-9554-80292538a40e\"><b>보신(補腎)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c864541-3ece-466d-a1eb-e31ed328d9bf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-eceb3006-cd6f-405e-b265-209e48903c1b\">녹용, 산수유, 복분자 등으로 신장의 정기(精氣)를 보강하여 기초 체력을 끌어올립니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef100459-08b3-47fe-a4a9-20f865ed1aed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f8db39cf-5d88-4959-84e3-764c3d0a50ac\"><b>청열해독(淸熱解毒)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0bf07a48-799b-4226-bf2a-62fdee0f0517\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b4f193ca-1afe-4320-b9ab-418191190026\">입안의 열감, 구취, 염증이 반복될 경우, 황련, 금은화 등의 약재로 열을 내려주어 신체의 염증 반응을 다스립니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-775da642-e2b7-44cb-826a-b8a1450c2e38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4bbd09c3-bdee-412f-a3ae-7dfbabb368dd\"><b>기혈순환 조절</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eb5f5c3c-1f8e-491c-95d9-71c554b88f5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d1819e4f-ad1e-49af-b875-f00005e872c4\">턱과 얼굴 주변의 순환을 돕기 위한 침 치료, 뜸, 온열요법 등이 함께 이루어지며 전신 컨디션 회복을 돕습니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-dbf7ea72-ffbb-449e-83e8-a2922d5d7ff7\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-071a39dc-932f-4a7c-96e5-6bd8b05f51a6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:490px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-071a39dc-932f-4a7c-96e5-6bd8b05f51a6\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/45ea1588912cc2d0.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"778\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/45ea1588912cc2d0.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/45ea1588912cc2d0.png\" data-width=\"490\" data-height=\"372\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-071a39dc-932f-4a7c-96e5-6bd8b05f51a6\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-717bbe63-ab8a-451a-96df-1de96627086f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-3f7753c4-5d0b-4475-bbb0-398194498e95\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8558185-a434-4f25-bf7e-e709d2f40a5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5561c6e5-d2ef-45d0-9116-7216ba0fee36\"><b>왜 고치법이 장수와 관련이 있을까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9d9209da-2481-4eac-8159-8f241d13fc5a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3172df99-6da4-49ef-9d3c-d03891345f6b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c4772d72-f6ce-4dc1-a1c1-9755740fae60\">고치법은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a46e8195-303d-4ad8-ae04-964266648131\"><b>증상만을 해결하는 치료가 아닙니다.</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5511beee-3594-4d66-ab15-264e0b3db34f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-89d987de-a5c3-4e79-ad2a-29ae7d992450\">신장 기능이 회복되면 단순히 입 안의 불편함이 사라지는 것에 그치지 않고,</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7ae9695c-5a3e-4450-8aea-11012c38e4ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-82867c45-5508-41f5-bdca-61fb00359a44\">체력이 덜 고갈되고</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2c95496-c63f-472b-b382-4b21d5694e57\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-557a7c01-2746-4524-a1d9-195897b201d8\">머리가 맑아지며</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae21fbeb-1d2a-406f-9883-6f978e7dbe4f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-17e59463-236a-4266-be2e-fd37383b7ff7\">소화기 기능이 좋아지고</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-69243d60-7fe0-46ee-8bd9-490aac4d1c99\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-56702fe9-871b-4005-966c-2a5afc0615ac\">면역력과 회복력도 향상됩니다.</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7224944e-82d1-45c5-ac32-81f64a6ba316\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0bc1be43-b7f3-4c80-ad9a-6e556262f9fa\">결국 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9e076391-c33e-47c7-aed0-9bd717333260\"><b>삶의 질을 지키고, 노화의 속도를 늦추는 치료법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7b2d5f94-d41a-4f48-9123-c7033b902962\">이라는 점에서, 고치법은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e45f4520-3182-4eaa-a590-6be22c6bcd78\"><b>장수를 위한 전통적 처방</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4eb00ad9-6795-4768-8800-867f1e373a97\">으로 여겨져 왔습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='